reviewText: 1996 (not 2016) lite feel good flick from Australia.  No real passion, ending is a joke. Nice music.

Aden Young plays a young man going the wrong way until his life is turned upside down when he is arriested and sentenced to 100 hours of community service. It may not b the best movie made but it is enjoyable and a movie  for all the family. Aden shows that he is a force to b noted of and a good actor.
